(226, 1, '2018-04-01 13:54:03', '2018-04-01 13:54:03', '<img class="aligncenter size-medium" src="https://s17.postimg.org/56eglgtlr/1522589384.png" width="360" height="342" />\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="16r02-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="16r02-0-0"><span data-offset-key="16r02-0-0">ASMA KE 17: AL-WAHHAB</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="ifs5-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="ifs5-0-0"><span data-offset-key="ifs5-0-0">(utk Kekayaan dan Wibawa)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="9nhf2-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="9nhf2-0-0"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="6p8v3-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="6p8v3-0-0"><span data-offset-key="6p8v3-0-0">* Barangsiapa mengekali berdzikir "Ya Wahhaab" setiap hari setiap lepas shalat 300x atau lebih, Insya Allah baginya kekayaan, kebesaran dan kuasa, kabul hajat dan hebat.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="2nc9f-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="2nc9f-0-0"><span data-offset-key="2nc9f-0-0">* Barangsiapa mengekali berdzikir dengan nya 40x pada akhir sujud shalat subuh, Insya Allah dimudahkan baginya kekayaan dan wibawa.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="2jtn6-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="2jtn6-0-0"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="ajm1f-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="ajm1f-0-0"><span data-offset-key="ajm1f-0-0">(Senjata Mu`min, KH. Husain Qadri, Martapura)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="f6hbn" data-offset-key="3of51-0-0">\r\n<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="3of51-0-0"><span da